body:
### Welcome to my GitHub Pages.
* 这个项目几乎是一个纸篓子,想到什么就扔什么进来.个人的平时工作的总结.很随性.
* 这些类大多是基于windows系统.现在也在转linux.

### Code Overview
* [跨平台socket简单封装类](https://github.com/cullet/xhblib/blob/master/msocketx.h)
* [跨平台线程类](https://github.com/cullet/xhblib/blob/master/mthread.h)
* [高性能日志类](https://github.com/cullet/xhblib/blob/master/logx.h)
* [高性能粒度内存池类](https://github.com/cullet/xhblib/blob/master/memoryx.h)
* [iocp模型封装](https://github.com/cullet/xhblib/blob/master/iocpx.h)
* 还有些小东西,如多线程锁,数据结构封装,数据库,平台特性,修改stl[等](https://github.com/cullet/xhblib).

```cpp
template<typename l_ = falselockx_,
	long ulmaxfilesize = 10 * 1024 * 1024,
	int nmaxlogfilenum = 10,
	int nflush = 1,	
	loghandlefn loghandT = loghandledefault>
class logx
{
public:
	logx()
	{
		m_nwritelevel = 0;
		m_nwritecount = 0;
		m_logbuff = NULL;
		m_stream = NULL;
		m_bstdout = true;
		memset(m_szfilename,0,sizeof(m_szfilename) * 
			sizeof(TCHAR));
		memset(m_szfolderpath,0,sizeof(m_szfolderpath) *
			sizeof(TCHAR));
	}
 	virtual ~logx()
 	{
 		CloseStream();
 		if (m_logbuff != NULL)
 		{
 			delete [] m_logbuff; 
 			m_logbuff = NULL;
 		}
		TCHAR* pfilename = NULL;
		while (pfilename = m_filequeue.pop_front())
		{
			delete [] pfilename;
		}
 	}
 };
```
